sorry i forgot to tell yall that i would be away but this time it was only for a week and i got back on saturday. sunday i went to a family thing upstate which was cute. yesterday was amazing as everyday w james i went over his house about 7 30 and chilled and waited for his cousin and we chilled for a little then watched Big Fish which was cool.  his little bro andrew ( who is sooo cute, he is 4 yrs old) partied w us which was cool. he is like a little bro to me ( i love that kid :-P .) yea so james was amazing :-D and then today kinda just sucked. i woke up at 12 and then went out for lunch shopped for lawn stuff then went home and chilled then tried to make plans and then got in trouble so that was put out and had to go out for dinner and that was just great. so i just got home from that whole mess. i hope i get to see james tomm <3 
love always, your friend,

Maggie k
